pep
===

pep is an utility to read, search, and maintain an updated local version
of Python Enhancement Proposals from command line.

Example usage :

 * pep 8 // To read the PEP 8
 * pep search guido // To search for 'guido' into PEPs
 * pep upgrade // To update local version of PEPs
 * pep upgrade with progress // To update local version showing the progression

Run `pep upgrade with progress` the first time to get a working local version.
